{"tid":2028184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史係一個循環，對方越急就會加速死亡","createTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T17:02:36.000Z","uid":12653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6745214bf62fc373791f433b1523b388a32bcdaf","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"二戰期間嘅日本，就係因為心急做錯一個偷襲珍珠港嘅決定，某程度上加快左整個二戰嘅結束<br />\n<br />\n希特拉因為心急，虛榮心而進攻列寧格勒呢種冇乜戰略意義嘅地方，忽視天氣而導致戰敗<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯戈巴卓夫，就係太心急推行改革導致蘇聯加速解體<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歷史從來話俾我哋知，心急總係唔會落得有好下場，唔該灰機撚死開。貪圖安逸就想改變現況係絕對冇可能！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c17c371404a6df3664fd78ef3e29d4e386198507","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"推比港豬睇"},{"pid":"558be8a8bc93e90b7c4ee5e42e1a8856f097766d","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17c371404a6df3664fd78ef3e29d4e386198507","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"推比港豬睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40715bb231e2ef5125addd2e31bd26a92531d691","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"推，振作"},{"pid":"c2e8d75086e5b129209ebf000ca0a158b88d9aee","tid":2028184,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"收到呢個消息，你可以頹一陣<br />\n但注意唔好俾五毛帶動風向<br />\n<br />\n只要你一驚，冇咗信心<br />\n就係對方贏咗"},{"pid":"fa5dbbd58edb746fe7b91d46c38c3fa70a9baeca","tid":2028184,"uid":336888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}